All of Tmplz's Exceptions are defined in this package and its sub-packages.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InternalException
    Should only be thrown as a result of a bug in Tmplz.
    TmplzException
    The base class for all of Tmplz's custom Exception classes.

Package org.tmotte.tmplz.exception Description

All of Tmplz's Exceptions are defined in this package and its sub-packages. The base class for all Exceptions is TmplzException, which is a RuntimeException because we are somewhat adverse to the hassles of checked Exceptions.
